 9.29 is out]]%0a%3c !!!18.4.2023%0a%3c '''Lexical Semantics'''%0a%3c * [[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lexical_semantics | Lexical Semantics]]%0a%3c * Attach:ChatGPT-vs-InfoCodex.pdf%0a%3c * Attach:Text_comprehension.pdf%0a%3c !!!11.4.2023%0a%3c '''dicom2gdt'''%0a%3c * [[https://github.com/zdavatz/gdt2dicom/releases | Convert DICOM files to GDT files]] with JPEG images.%0a%3c !!!3.4.2023%0a%3c '''Teilabgabe von Medikamenten'''%0a%3c * Attach:Q&A_Taskforce-Teilabgabe_von_Medikamenten.pdf%0a%3c * Den Beipackzettel gibt es einfach und schnell mit einem Scan vom [[https://apps.apple.com/ch/app/generika/id520038123 | Generika App]].%0a%3c !!!31.3.2023%0a%3c '''Machine learning'''%0a%3c * Machine learning: [[Ywesee/CreationDiscoveryIntelligence | creation, discovery... intelligence]]?%0a%3c !!!15.3.2023%0a%3c '''gdt2dicom'''%0a%3c * Convert GDT files and a folder of JPEG images to a DICOM file with [[https://github.com/zdavatz/gdt2dicom | gdt2dicom]].%0a%3c !!!5.3.2023%0a%3c '''Semantics outperform Grammar'''%0a%3c * [[Ywesee/SemanticsOutperformGrammar | Semantics outperform Grammar]]%0a%3c !!!28.2.2023%0a%3c '''Miele-LXIV'''%0a%3c * Miele-LXIV for Windows is out, Attach:Miele-LXIV-0.6.1147.zip%0a%3c !!!27.2.2023%0a%3c '''AmiKo iOS'''%0a%3c * Update 2.9.85 for [[AmiKo/IOS |AmiKo iOS]] is out.%0a%3c !!!23.2.2023%0a%3c '''Semantics vs Grammar'''%0a%3c * [[Ywesee/SemanticeVsGrammar | Semantics vs Grammar]]%0a%3c !!!3.2.2023%0a%3c '''Semantics Trumps Grammar'''%0a%3c * [[Ywesee/SemanticsTrumpsGrammar | Semantics Trumps Grammar]] - [[https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/semantics-trumps-grammar-zeno-ramun-raphael-davatz/ | Linkedin]]%0a%3c !!!30.1.2023%0a%3c '''Generika Android App'''%0a%3c * [[https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.oddb.generika&hl=de&gl=US | Generika App für Android]] hat jetzt MinSdkVersion 23 und TargetSdkVersion 31%0a%3c !!!26.1.2023%0a%3c '''emedswiss SA'''%0a%3c * [[https://www.emedswiss.ch/ | emedswiss SA]] is using [[https://www.hin.ch/services/